Mailalytics: Mail Analytics Project
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Chart #1: X people sent Y Messages
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This could be used to create three histograms.  This shows how many people sent
a certain number 1) messages, 2) new messages, and 3) replies.  In this
representation, Total is independent from New and Replies therefore in this
case Total != New + Replies.

  | Total | New | Replies
-------------------------
1 |   5   |  4  |   3
2 |   6   |  2  |   3
3 |   9   |  4  |   4

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Chart #2: Y number of threads of size X
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This attempts to look at the engagement based on a histogram of the length of
conversations.

# Threads | Size |
---------------------------------------
    1     |  11  |
    2     |  13  |
    3     |  15  |
    4     |  17  |

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
